org.jamplate.impl.parser

Class MergeByWeightParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jamplate.impl.parser.MergeByWeightParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parser
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MergeFlatByWeightParser

    public class MergeByWeightParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements Parser
    A parser that uses multiple other parsers for parsing. Any clash in the results returned from them will be fixed by taking the results of the more preferred parser on the clash depending on a predefined list.
    Since:
    0.2.0 ~2021.05.17
    Version:
    0.2.0
    Author:
    LSafer
